    excerpt: 'Doha has an impressive collection of rooftop bars offering dramatic skyline and Gulf views. From the iconic Sky View at the Four Seasons to the lively outdoor terrace at Iris on The Pearl, here is your complete guide to the best elevated drinking spots in the city.',
